headline: Trane Technologies (TT) Unveils BrainBox AI Lab for Sustainable Energy Optimization
summary: Trane Technologies (TT) has recently launched the BrainBox AI Lab, aiming to revolutionize energy optimization in HVAC solutions and refrigerated transport, aligning with its sustainability goals. Over the last quarter, the company's stock price saw a modest increase of 1.47%, which mirrors the broader market trends where both the S&P 500 and Nasdaq hit all-time highs. headline: TT Q2 Deep Dive: Commercial HVAC Strength Offsets Residential Headwinds, Guidance Raised
summary: HVAC company Trane (NYSE:TT) met Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q2 CY2025, with sales up 8.3% year on year to $5.75 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $3.88 per share was 2.3% above analysts’ consensus estimates.
